mages, open images with other applications like an image-editor or configure an image as the desktop wallpaper.kscreenshotsüxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/xfce/ristretto/f2df290130ab77a925dfb62f209189ec/screenshots/image-1_orig.pnggversionf0.13.2ldownload_urlxwhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/ristretto-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.54 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTCjcategoriesoGraphics,Viewer”cpkgvpcmanfm.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namegPcmanfmfpkg_idx8github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.pcmanfm-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxuhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/pcmanfm-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.20 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkgtpcsx2.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_nameePcsx2fpkg_idx6github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.pcsx2-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxshttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/pcsx2-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizei148.85 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkgvpolybar.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namegPolybarfpkg_idx8github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.polybar-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxuhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/polybar-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.16 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC©cpkgxquake3e (engine).dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namepQuake3e (Engine)fpkg_idx8github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.quake3e-29_05_2025-xplshnkdescriptionwQuake 3 Enhanced enginepdescription_longyķThis is a modern Quake III Arena engine aimed to be fast, secure and compatible with all existing Q3A mods. It is based on last non-SDL source dump of ioquake3 with latest upstream fixes applied.

Key features:

* Optimized OpenGL renderer
* Optimized Vulkan renderer
* Raw mouse input support, enabled automatically instead of DirectInput(\in_mouse 1) if available
* Unlagged mouse events processing, can be reverted by setting \in_lagged 1
* \in_minimize - hotkey for minimize/restore main window (win32-only, direct replacement for Q3Minimizer)
* \video-pipe - to use external ffmpeg binary as an encoder for better quality and smaller output files
* Significantly reworked QVM (Quake Virtual Machine)
* Improved server-side DoS protection, much reduced memory usage
* Raised filesystem limits (up to 20,000 maps can be handled in a single directory)
* Reworked Zone memory allocator, no more out-of-memory errors
* Non-intrusive support for SDL2 backend (video, audio, input), selectable at compile time
* Tons of bug fixes and other improvements
* Vulkan renderer based on Quake-III-Arena-Kenny-Edition with many additions:

* High-quality per-pixel dynamic lighting
* Very fast flares (\r_flares 1)
* Anisotropic filtering (\r_ext_texture_filter_anisotropic)
* Greatly reduced API overhead (call/dispatch ratio)
* Flexible vertex buffer memory management to allow loading huge maps
* Multiple command buffers to reduce processing bottlenecks
* Reversed depth buffer to eliminate z-fighting on big maps
* Merged lightmaps (atlases)
* Multitexturing optimizations
* Static world surfaces cached in VBO (\r_vbo 1)
* Useful debug markers for tools like RenderDoc
* Fixed framebuffer corruption on some Intel iGPUs
* Offscreen rendering, enabled with \r_fbo 1, all following requires it enabled:

* ScreenMap texture rendering - to create realistic environment reflections
* Multisample anti-aliasing (\r_ext_multisample)
* Supersample anti-aliasing (\r_ext_supersample)
* Per-window gamma-correction which is important for screen-capture tools like OBS
* You can minimize game window any time during \video|\video-pipe recording
* High dynamic range render targets (\r_hdr 1) to avoid color banding
* Bloom post-processing effect
* Arbitrary resolution rendering
* Greyscale modeldownload_urlxchttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/quake3e.dwfs.AppBundledsizeg8.36 MBjbuild_datex2025-05-29 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkguscrcpy.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namefScrcpyfpkg_idx7github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.scrcpy-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxthttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/scrcpy-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh39.53 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkguthunar.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namefThunarfpkg_idx7github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.thunar-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxthttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/thunar-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.42 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkgxxfce4-multicall.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_nameoXfce4 Multicallfpkg_idx@github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-multicall-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlx}https://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/xfce4-multicall-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh18.22 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkgx"xfce4-power-manager.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namesXfce4 Power Managerfpkg_idxDgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-power-manager-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxühttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/xfce4-power-manager-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.16 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkgx"xfce4-screenshooter.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namesXfce4 Screenshooterfpkg_idxDgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-screenshooter-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxühttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/xfce4-screenshooter-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.11 MBjbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTC”cpkgx xfce4-taskmanager.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_nameqXfce4 Taskmanagerfpkg_idxBgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-taskmanager-27_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/release